    "sentence": "又言吐蕃必無信約，專須防備，不可輕易。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000116",
    "sentence": "上每善遇之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000117",
    "sentence": "倫居家孝友，撫弟侄以慈愛稱。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000118",
    "sentence": "貞元十四年十二月卒，時年八十三，贈揚州都督。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "十四年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 5
      },
      {
        "text": "贈揚州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 16,
        "end": 19
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000119",
    "sentence": "賈耽",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000120",
    "sentence": "賈耽，字敦詩，滄州南皮人。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "滄州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 7,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000121",
    "sentence": "以兩經登第，調授貝州臨清縣尉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "調授貝州臨清縣",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 13
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000122",
    "sentence": "上疏論時政，授絳州正平尉。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "授絳州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 6,
        "end": 9
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000123",
    "sentence": "從事河東，檢校膳部員外郎、太原少尹、北都副留守。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000124",
    "sentence": "又檢校禮部郎中、節度副使，改汾州刺史。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "改汾州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 13,
        "end": 16
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 16,
        "end": 18
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000125",
    "sentence": "在郡七年，政績茂異。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "在郡",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 0,
        "end": 2
      },
      {
        "text": "七年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000126",
    "sentence": "入為鴻臚卿，時左右威遠營隸鴻臚，耽仍領其使。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000127",
    "sentence": "大歷十四年十一月，檢校左散騎常侍、兼梁州刺史、御史大夫、山南西道節度使。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "十四年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 5
      },
      {
        "text": "兼梁州",
        "label": "LOC",
        "start": 17,
        "end": 20
      },
      {
        "text": "刺史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 20,
        "end": 22
      },
      {
        "text": "御史",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 23,
        "end": 25
      },
      {
        "text": "大夫",
        "label": "TITLE",
        "start": 25,
        "end": 27
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_008_138_000128",
    "sentence": "建中三年十一月，檢校工部尚書、兼御史大夫、山南東道節度使。",
    "entities": [
      {
        "text": "三年",
        "label": "TME",
        "start": 2,
        "end": 4
      },
      {
        "text": "尚書",
